_🗄️ Data Integrity & Integration_ | _🟠 Major_ | _⚡ Quick win_

**Include the fields emitted by all list APIs in the shared contract.**

`SessionListEntry` omits `title`, but `listOpencodeSessions()` returns it in `src/helpers/session-context-opencode.ts` Lines 112-115. Typed callers of `SessionListResult` cannot rely on the documented/runtime opencode payload.

<details>
<summary>Proposed fix</summary>

```diff
 export interface SessionListEntry {
   id: string;
+  title?: string;
   updatedAt: string;
 }
```
</details>

